{"tid":464270,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟呢D女人咩心態","createTime":"2017-11-10T11:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T11:31:52.000Z","uid":59053,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a303c6ffc6d4b7962d426e349a5ff70140874d3d","tid":464270,"uid":59053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"我1個月前飛左條女，原因佢唔肯化妝打扮，叫佢著短裙仔又唔肯，一字肩又唔肯，著40D黑絲又唔肯，重要床上又唔主動，又唔肯含，頂唔順飛左佢。<br />\n<br />\n近排佢識左條新仔，成個人變哂，變哂我鍾意既類型。又化哂妝，又短裙又黑絲又戰鬥格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nD女人真係好恐怖，已經唔敢想像佢床上會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 好撚想返啅，求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6b11ff0acb1662abc36c7a35da5d9409e9c802","tid":464270,"uid":72979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"26a77394ce9b9de00848734557bfe1b97eca196d","tid":464270,"uid":124677,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:11:22.000Z","msg":"唔係女人咩心態<br />\n係你無能力吸引力令到佢咁做<br />\n女人絕對會為一個值得去愛既人改變<br />\n<br />\n散嗰陣咁瀟灑 依家後悔?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9fbf78a46066c73d9679b0e6483198958a89cd","tid":464270,"uid":102703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:29:28.000Z","msg":"笑左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369